des: "This delicious dip was sold at a local meat market where I used to live.  Since I no longer live in that area, I decided to try and duplicate the taste. I have substituted Italian 4-cheese blend for the Parmesan with success. For best flavor, let sit over night."
ins: Blend the feta cheese, Parmesan cheese, cream cheese, and sun-dried tomato pesto in a food processor until completely mixed. Serve immediately or chill overnight.
